data.description: NEW PRICE!   SOLAR!  MT VIEWS! This 1479 square foot home has 2 x 6 construction, boasts 3 bedrooms EACH with its own walk-in closet, 2 full baths, open concept floor plan, separate laundry room with shelving, custom tile work in the kitchen and both bathrooms and a spacious two-car garage with insulated garage door. The recently painted garage accommodates trucks and/or sports utility vehicles with additional storage space. Beautiful backyard with custom basketball court. REFRIGERATED central air conditioning supported by a solar panel system for electric utilities savings. Sellers have contracted with America's Preferred HOME WARRANTY that transfers to the new owners at closing for a full year. Alarm system too!Low maintenance front and backyards with drip systems. Come take a look!
